 visible is committed to helping our neighbors thrive by engaging in commun
 ity service projects that address the needs of the vulnerable. Our Sandwic
 h Project will benefit Cathedral Kitchen. We will provide all the material
 s\; all you need to do is bring willing hands to do the work.
